No fewer than ten passengers including the driver of an eighteen seater bus were on Tuesday abducted along Akure/ Ikere Ekiti road by unknown gunmen. The bus was travelling to Ado-Ekiti from Akure before it was ambushed at one of the bad spots on the route. The heavily armed suspected kidnappers were said to have waylaid a commercial bus along the road and took the passengers to an unknown place. Details Shortlyâ€¦